    • withAuthSession

      public HTTPClient withAuthSession(AuthSession session)
      Description copied from interface: RESTClient
      Returns a REST client that authenticates requests using the given session.

      Implementation requirements:

      • Closing the returned client SHOULD NOT affect this client: if they share common resources, the resources SHOULD NOT be closed until the parent client is closed.
      • Closing the returned client SHOULD NOT close the given AuthSession: this is the responsibility of this method's caller.
